snippet.title: Forget Me Not: Palette trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for the PSX game Forget Me Not: Palette. Palette was originally a freeware adventure game made with RPG Maker 95, it was highly acclaimed in the Fourth ASCII Entertainment Software Contest which resulted in the game being remade for the PlayStation by Enterbrain.
